K10d发布于2006年9月13日，<ref>{{cite press release | url = http://www.pentaximaging.com/footer/news_media_article?ArticleId=8794568 | publisher = Pentax imaging | date = 2006-09-13 | title = Pentax announces K10D digital SLR with ten megapixels, shake reduction and weather-resistant body | access-date = 2006-09-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20061010082749/http://www.pentaximaging.com/footer/news_media_article?ArticleId=8794568 | archive-date = 2006-10-10 | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 并且在同年11月中旬开始正式销售,而三星GX-10则发布于2006年9月21日<ref>{{Cite press release | url = http://www.dpreview.com/news/0609/06092101samsunggx10.asp | title = Samsung SLR evolves with the launch of the GX-10 | publisher = Samsung | date = 2006-09-21 | access-date = 2010-09-22 | archive-date = 2011-10-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111018221135/http://dpreview.com/news/0609/06092101samsunggx10.asp | dead-url = no }}</ref>并于2007年1月1日开始发售。宾得K10d的后继机型[[宾得_K20D|宾得 K20D]]，于2008年1月23日发布。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pentaximaging.com/products/product_details/digital_camera--K20D/reqID--10505894/subsection--digital_slr|title=K20D Digital SLR|publisher=Pentax|date=2008-01-23|accessdate=2010-09-22|archive-date=2008-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080513141307/http://www.pentaximaging.com/products/product_details/digital_camera--K20D/reqID--10505894/subsection--digital_slr|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

